high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn left, go to the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Go around the table and go to the sink, turn left and go to the counter
Slice the potato on the counter
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the microwave
Put the knife on the counter to the right of microwave
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the counter
Pick a potato slice from the counter
Turn left, go forward a bit, turn left and go to the fridge
Put the potato slice in the fridge, wait, pick up the potato slice from the fridge
Turn right, go forward a bit, turn right and go to the microwave
Put the potato slice on the counter to the right of microwave
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, cool a slice of potato

high_descs: Turn right, walk towards the wall, then turn left towards the round table.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn left, walk towards the sink, and then turn left to the potato on the counter.
Slice the potato into pieces.
Turn left and head towards the counter where the microwave is at.
Place the knife to the right of the spoon on the counter.
Turn right and head towards the toaster.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge.
Place the slice of potato on the top shelf inside the fridge, let it cool, and take it back out.
Turn around and walk towards the microwave.
Place the potato in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of cool potato along with a knife on the counter close to the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, cross room to wall, walk left to round table.
Pick up the table knife from the table.
Turn left,  head toward garbage can, turn right, walk to sink, turn left, go to counter to left of sink with potato on it.
Slice the potato that is on the counter.
Turn left, turn left, go to counter, turn right, walk to microwave, turn right to face it.
Put the knife down to the right of the spoon.
Turn around to the left until you face sink, cross room to sink, walk to counter with potato.
Pick up one potato slice from the counter.
Turn right, turn right at sink,  turn left, walk to refrigerator.
Put potato slice in refrigerator door, wait a few seconds, open door, take out potato slice.
Turn right, walk to table, take zigzag path to counter with microwave.
Put the potato slice on the counter in front of and to right of microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of potato on the counter.
